{"tid":622285,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"虛幣低點已到？傳索羅斯基金準備進場，比特幣彈高","createTime":"2018-04-09T04:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T05:41:50.000Z","uid":55200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3605e6334f77ae1eb38af7ae15c1e09de88bc55f","tid":622285,"uid":55200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:47:09.000Z","msg":"虛擬貨幣熱潮退燒，價格自高點腰斬，據傳金融巨鱷索羅準備趁著低點悄悄進場，購入比特幣，激勵價格反彈。<br />\n<br />\nFortune、Cointelegraph 6日引述外電消息稱，消息人士透露，索羅斯基金管理公司(Soros Fund Management)的全球總經投資主管Adam Fisher，已經取得內部許可得以從事虛幣交易，不過他尚未進場。<br />\n<br />\n如果謠傳為真，索羅斯也許打算逢低買進。虛幣正值風雨飄搖之際，價格從2017年底的2萬美元、如今跌掉一半以上。各國加強監管，嚇退投資人，導致價格持續重挫。Hedge Fund Research研究顯示，今年第一季，直接投資各種虛幣的基金，價值平均暴跌52%。相較之下，同一時期避險基金(主要投資股票)平均報酬為0.4%。<br />\n<br />\n其實索羅斯早早就布局虛幣概念股，<a href=\"http://他旗下的基金公司去年成了Overstock.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%96%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86Overstock.com&d=Mq2wWObIBZX4gLhDb%2F3GPAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=ab4446eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">他旗下的基金公司去年成了Overstock.com</a>的第三大股東。<a href=\"http://Overstock.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOverstock.com&d=Mq2wWObIBZX4gLhDb%2F3GPAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=162e4126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Overstock.com</a>是第一家接受比特幣付款的大型零售商。<br />\n<br />\n由此看來，索羅斯似乎心口不一，他今年1月25日才在瑞士達沃斯(Davos)的世界經濟論壇砲轟比特幣，當時他說比特幣波動太大，不該被視為貨幣。貨幣應該是穩定的價值儲藏(store of value)工具，比特幣可能在一天內震盪25%，不適合拿來支付薪水，這樣會讓薪水一夕間縮水25%。比特幣是基於誤解的投機。<br />\n<br />\n索羅斯有意投資的消息6日傳出後，比特幣價格上漲、從6,600美元重回7,000美元左右(見附圖)。Coindesk報價顯示，台北時間9日上午9點22分，比特幣上揚0.89%、報7,085.47美元。"},{"pid":"79856912cd93ce868fb05648dce57b6332be1732","tid":622285,"uid":51933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"人地都無講過係long<br />\n可能做short呢"},{"pid":"ee8bf5372d9bcc95cb0f865c4195231a278c23ec","tid":622285,"uid":76063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"傳! 引人買cap埋呢浸"},{"pid":"2c3f2413d664ffab99ffa9773ca04d749a4a3419","tid":622285,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"消息人士透露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e749e8cfbcc272bbd66189e5f13d178929d9149f","tid":622285,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"比得你知個時都著埋草"},{"pid":"035f7529921ef049167bd28dee112299f4325988","tid":622285,"uid":92459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"尚未進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係自己都未食，就俾你地食先?"},{"pid":"4c0216e8c9bbe712f7c16027bdcb189933376311","tid":622285,"uid":109386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:27:05.000Z","msg":"我下星期會買，你地快d托高個價先，我再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3e1899873f95b14d0e9c1d80234d84523c1abb","tid":622285,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"索羅斯原本想買btn，但聽到燈神打哥想買，索老應該收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf007ba30b56eaf67c64e827be362fce69988d2","tid":622285,"uid":90772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"索羅斯：「嗱就咁的，我聽日中午就會買bitcoin」姐係好似做戲入面，準備打人開戰嗰陣鳩叫咁。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲垃圾新聞，信嗰個係咪要驗驗腦"},{"pid":"0915b669f0cd02f81ba542cc5ee227812f3726ce","tid":622285,"uid":55200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"彈完俾人沽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dd71e59840d1c1588804c634769490eeb3816f","tid":622285,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"虛擬貨幣又大跌！比特幣插半成　低見6718美元<br />\n<br />\n04月09日(一) 22:26<br />\n<br />\n虛擬貨幣又大跌！有交易平台報價顯示，「一哥」比特幣現報6,718美元，短短約兩小時勁跌357美元或5%。自3月以來，比特幣已累插逾27%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有分析指出，今次比特幣遭到拋售與美國交稅季節來臨有關。比特幣大好友、華爾街資深分析師、Fundstrat Global Advisors策略師Tom Lee上周估計，美國家庭仍欠虛擬貨幣大約250億美元資本增值稅，需要沽貨套現，或直至4月15日交稅限期為止，故造成大量沽壓。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"16d1f9f3c33f2b3b8eec4e05637db9837b94633e","tid":622285,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"Warren buffet vs George Soros？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926acb6e8c4627ea573fdc6ecdb6c320540adae8","tid":622285,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:22:08.000Z","msg":"都唔係直接掃bitcoin <br />\n佢直接掃bitcoin 先算啦"},{"pid":"2f0fcb54280bff48d3816f96d3afde972e45ec48","tid":622285,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3f2413d664ffab99ffa9773ca04d749a4a3419","tid":622285,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"消息人士透露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:11:25.000Z","msg":"街邊師奶..."},{"pid":"81a25cec4fe306b338b1db18fede14477bb8389f","tid":622285,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"咁準？"},{"pid":"108687249e84d2ad6b0f7d548364bc639cd31809","tid":622285,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"索羅斯沽美股輸到pk"},{"pid":"aa5cbdc78c2a818f83192a512b0c2cad463d477f","tid":622285,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"尋日嗰下 1000 連record volume 係勁嘅"}]}